original_client_text.markup_text:
Unboxing the AirPods Pro 2 (with USB-C!)🎧

After my original AirPods Pro started acting up with a static sound in both earbuds, I knew it was time for an upgrade. Even though I have the AirPods Max, I still needed a portable option with solid noise cancellation and the second gen Pros were the obvious pick.

Excited to finally try out Adaptive Transparency, Personalized Spatial Audio, and the upgraded Active Noise Cancellation. And the best part? USB-C charging! I’m almost free from lightning cables, only the AirPods Max left to go.

What AirPods are you using? Let me know!

.
.
.

#airpods #airpodspro #airpodspro2 #noisecancelling #usbc
